  - `hash_field_ttl_ms(key, field, now_ms) -> HashFieldTtl` returning Missing/NoTtl/Remaining(ms)/Expired.
  - `hash_field_persist(key, field) -> HashFieldPersistResult`.
  - `drop_hash_field_if_expired(key, field, now_ms)` (internal).
  - `clear_hash_field_ttls_on_hdel` hook for existing HDEL sites (wired in part 3).
- Unit tests in fr-store tests/ for: set-get-persist roundtrip; NX/XX/GT/LT; expired-field detection; key-deletion removes all field TTLs.

No fr-command commands yet (part 2). No encoding / RDB changes yet (part 4). No command-integration (part 3).", "status": "closed", "priority": 1, "issue_type": "task", "created_at": "2026-04-23T22:57:42.284981206Z", "created_by": "ubuntu", "updated_at": "2026-04-23T23:02:20.625335597Z", "closed_at": "2026-04-23T23:02:20.623470537Z", "close_reason": "Landed in f700569: per-field TTL storage on Store with NX/XX/GT/LT-aware setter, unit-aware HTTL/HEXPIRETIME readers, HPERSIST semantics, and HDEL/whole-key cleanup hooks. 16 unit tests pass; fr-store overall 280/0. Downstream parts 2/3/4 (c0z9, b8ut, 3jrv) consume these primitives.", "source_repo": ".", "compaction_level": 0, "original_size": 0}
